# 🌍 TravelWorld

**A Fullstack Tours & Travels Web App Using MERN Stack 💫**

---

## 🔗 Live Preview

**Live Demo:** [travelworld.shuence.com](https://travelworld.shuence.com)

---

## 📦 Environment Variables

Add the following to your `.env` file in the frontend directory:

```
REACT_APP_BASE_URL=http://localhost:4000/api/v1
```

---

## ✨ Features

- **Tours Listing**: Display a list of available tours for users to explore.
- **Featured Tours**: Highlight special/popular tours on the homepage.
- **Tour Details**: Description, itinerary, price, and more.
- **Gallery**: High-quality images and videos of destinations.
- **User Authentication**: User registration and login.
- **Booking System**: Secure online tour booking.
- **Search Tours**: Search for tours by keyword or filter.
- **Reviews and Ratings**: Users can leave feedback.
- **Responsive Design**: Optimized across all screen sizes.
- **Newsletter Signup**: Email updates and promotions.
- **User Testimonials**: Display customer reviews.
- **Contact Form**: Easy inquiries or feedback.
- **Blogs**: Informational blog posts for users.
- **Alerts**: Real-time error and success notifications.
- **FAQs**: Common questions answered.
- **Google Analytics**: Integrated for insights.

