## 💻 Setup Instructions

### ✅ Prerequisites

- Node.js installed
- MongoDB running (locally or cloud)

### 📥 Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/travelworld.git
cd travelworld
```

### 🖥️ Frontend Setup

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm start
```

### 🔧 Backend Setup

```bash
cd backend
npm install
npm run dev
```

